name: FEngineServicePong
doc: Implements a message for responding to a request to discover engine instances on the network.

CurrentLevel: Holds the name of the currently loaded level, if any.
HasBegunPlay: Holds a flag indicating whether game play has begun.
InstanceType: Holds the type of the engine instance.
SessionId: Holds the identifier of the session that the application belongs to.
WorldTimeSeconds: Holds the time in seconds since the world was loaded.
